Welcome to Martins Distribution Invoice Processing Application

This application is intended to be used to extract the information from a pdf file of an invoice into relevant values that can be exported to 
our clients as csv. 

- The command to turn this project into a single executable file is the following: 

  pyinstaller ^
      --onefile ^
      --windowed ^
      --clean ^
      --noconfirm ^
      --icon="Martins-Distribution_RGB.ico" ^
      --collect-all tkinterdnd2 ^
      --collect-all pydantic_core ^
      --collect-all pymupdf ^
      --add-data "Martins-Distribution_RGB.ico;." ^
      MDIP.py

Once this is run you will have MDIP.exe (Martins Distribution Invoice Processing) executable file ready to be downloaded on any device. 
